# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# Access-land data — large and regeneratable, so kept OUT of git history.
#   assets/access/      source GeoJSON, rebuilt with spike/fetch_access.mjs
#   assets/packs/*.geojson  region packs, rebuilt with spike/build_pack.mjs
#                           (or downloaded from GitHub Releases)
# The tiny index files (manifest.json, coverage.geojson) ARE tracked so the app
# always knows what regions exist. After cloning, regenerate the data — see
# DATA.md.
/assets/access/
/assets/packs/*.geojson
!/assets/packs/coverage.geojson
